# Android app only (NOK Super)

- **Primary focus:** Capacitor **Android app** (`android/`, `www/` as bundled assets). The team is **not** doing general website work right now.
- **Do not** change pages/CSS/JS for **browser-only** reasons unless the user **explicitly** requests it.
- When changing shared `www/` files for the app, **prefer app-only behavior**: e.g. `window.Capacitor`, `html.android-app-home`, or native Android code — so the website in a normal browser stays as-is.
- After `www/` edits for the app, remind to run **`npx cap sync android`** and rebuild in Android Studio.
